holy places from israeli occupation 
we had never imagined that the preservation of the legal and 
administrative links between the two banks could constitute an 
obstacle to the liberation of the occupied palestinian land 
yet lately it has transpired that there is a general palestinian 
and arab orientation towards highlighting the palestinian identity 
in a complete manner in every effort or activity related to the 
palestinian question and its developments 
jordans maintaining links with the west bank contradicts this 
orientation and hampers the palestinian strugle to gain 
international support for the palestinian cause as the national 
cause of a people struggling against foreign occupation 
</TEXT>
